01:14:05.720 --> 01:14:08.025
<i>absolutely nothing.</i>

1229
01:14:11.498 --> 01:14:15.373
Are you okay. Melanie?
Can we get you a-a water?

1230
01:14:15.406 --> 01:14:18.646
[intense music]

1231
01:14:23.088 --> 01:14:25.059
[dramatic music]

1232
01:14:40.624 --> 01:14:43.563
A wiretap. ladies and gentlemen.

1233
01:14:43.597 --> 01:14:48.305
is a weapon of choice
for lazy prosecutors.

1234
01:14:48.339 --> 01:14:52.814
[Tacopina] In my client's case.
detectives used Dr. Miller

1235
01:14:52.848 --> 01:14:55.554
to question her by proxy.

1236
01:14:55.587 --> 01:14:58.993
<i>forcing the man
she trusted most</i>

1237
01:14:59.027 --> 01:15:02.601
to catch her
at her most vulnerable.

1238
01:15:02.634 --> 01:15:05.974
without the benefit of counsel.

1239
01:15:06.008 --> 01:15:11.151
Remember. Ms. Prezioso
maintains. without evidence.

1240
01:15:11.184 --> 01:15:13.188
<i>that Dr. Miller was Melanie's</i>

1241
01:15:13.222 --> 01:15:16.328
<i>entire motive
for killing her husband.</i>

1242
01:15:16.361 --> 01:15:19.200
And yet I ask you.

1243
01:15:19.234 --> 01:15:21.840
where on those many tapes

1244
01:15:21.873 --> 01:15:25.179
<i>recorded during
raw and intimate moments</i>

1245
01:15:25.212 --> 01:15:29.087
<i>does my client admit
or even imply.</i>

1246
01:15:29.120 --> 01:15:31.458
she had anything to do

1247
01:15:31.492 --> 01:15:34.230
with Bill McGuire's death?

1248
01:15:35.801 --> 01:15:37.738
Nowhere.

1249
01:15:37.771 --> 01:15:39.675
Even as Dr. Miller

1250
01:15:39.709 --> 01:15:43.749
pressed her over and over
for the confession

1251
01:15:43.783 --> 01:15:47.624
Ms. Prezioso
so desperately wanted...

1252
01:15:47.658 --> 01:15:51.566
While Dr. Miller was making
those recordings.

1253
01:15:51.599 --> 01:15:54.738
he was still seeing my client.

1254
01:15:54.772 --> 01:15:58.647
<i>He was still trusting her.
he was still loving her.</i>

1255
01:15:58.680 --> 01:16:02.888
<i>despite everything these
detectives were telling him.</i>

1256
01:16:04.057 --> 01:16:08.265
Those recordings
only exonerate my client.

1257
01:16:08.299 --> 01:16:13.308
They show the true.
the unguarded Melanie McGuire.

1258
01:16:13.341 --> 01:16:15.814
Imperfect? Yes.

1259
01:16:15.848 --> 01:16:20.758
Seeking refuge from a cruel
and violent husband...

1260
01:16:20.791 --> 01:16:23.697
-[indistinct yelling]
-Don't touch me! Don't...

1261
01:16:23.730 --> 01:16:26.201
But a depraved killer?

1262
01:16:26.234 --> 01:16:27.704
No way.

1263
01:16:28.372 --> 01:16:29.675
Never.

1264
01:16:30.476 --> 01:16:32.180
So let's be done with all this.

1265
01:16:32.213 --> 01:16:36.723
We can grieve the victim.
and we absolutely should.

1266
01:16:36.756 --> 01:16:39.729
But. members of the jury.
I ask you.

1267
01:16:39.762 --> 01:16:43.970
end this persecution
of an innocent woman.

1268
01:16:45.306 --> 01:16:48.646
Melanie McGuire is not guilty

1269
01:16:48.679 --> 01:16:50.683
of this crime.

1270
01:16:50.717 --> 01:16:53.957
Allow her to get on
with her life.

1271
01:16:53.990 --> 01:16:59.167
Allow her to go home
to her children.

1272
01:17:01.504 --> 01:17:03.041
Thank you.

1273
01:17:22.080 --> 01:17:23.381
I gotta be honest.

1274
01:17:23.415 --> 01:17:28.091
keeping up with the defendant's
fantastical account

1275
01:17:28.125 --> 01:17:32.400
over the past two years
has been a full-time job.

1276
01:17:32.433 --> 01:17:33.869
But. thankfully.

1277
01:17:33.903 --> 01:17:37.109
she can't lie her way
out of DNA.

1278
01:17:37.143 --> 01:17:41.586
Can't spin the human sawdust
she tracked into Bill's car

1279
01:17:41.619 --> 01:17:44.591
after cutting him to pieces.

1280
01:17:44.625 --> 01:17:46.495
You need nothing more
to convict her.

1281
01:17:46.529 --> 01:17:49.969
but there's even more.

1282
01:17:50.002 --> 01:17:51.338
and you have it in abundance.

1283
01:17:51.371 --> 01:17:55.880
starting with the fact
that there was no fight.

1284
01:17:59.521 --> 01:18:03.195
In the early hours
of April 28th. 2004.

1285
01:18:03.229 --> 01:18:05.132
there was no fight.

1286
01:18:05.166 --> 01:18:07.737
No. Bill never sped off
in his car.

1287
01:18:07.771 --> 01:18:11.444
No. instead.
he lay in a stupor...

1288
01:18:13.315 --> 01:18:15.118
<i>from the chloral hydrate</i>

1289
01:18:15.152 --> 01:18:18.191
<i>that the autopsy found
in his bloodstream.</i>

1290
01:18:19.528 --> 01:18:21.397
Incapacitated...

1291
01:18:23.102 --> 01:18:27.176
by the date-rape drug
that Melanie used to poison him.

1292
01:18:27.209 --> 01:18:30.182
[intense music]

1293
01:18:31.619 --> 01:18:34.792
What happened next took two days

1294
01:18:34.825 --> 01:18:39.233
and it. it is not
for the faint of heart.

1295
01:18:40.603 --> 01:18:42.874
[gunshots]

1296
01:18:44.310 --> 01:18:46.516
[intense music]

1297
01:18:46.549 --> 01:18:48.620
[machine whirring]

1298
01:18:48.653 --> 01:18:51.592
[music continues]

1299
01:18:51.625 --> 01:18:54.798
[machine whirring]

1300
01:18:57.538 --> 01:18:59.274
A seven-hour drive. now just

1301
01:18:59.307 --> 01:19:01.011
think about that.
ladies and gentlemen.

1302
01:19:01.044 --> 01:19:03.315
[Patti] <i>Seven hours in a car</i>

1303
01:19:03.349 --> 01:19:06.623
with her husband
stuffed into suitcases

1304
01:19:06.656 --> 01:19:09.160
in the back of her SUV.

1305
01:19:14.404 --> 01:19:16.776
Did she reflect in horror
on what she had done?

1306
01:19:16.810 --> 01:19:20.049
<i>Uh. show any remorse
whatsoever?</i>

1307
01:19:20.082 --> 01:19:22.888
No. her actions tell us
that she did not.

1308
01:19:22.921 --> 01:19:26.695
because Melanie's last act
that night

1309
01:19:26.729 --> 01:19:30.002
was to throw out
the father of her children...

1310
01:19:31.104 --> 01:19:33.408
like she was throwing out
the trash.

1311
01:19:34.845 --> 01:19:36.982
[water splashes]

1312
01:19:39.855 --> 01:19:43.128
[Devesa] Ladies and gentlemen
of the jury.

1313
01:19:43.161 --> 01:19:46.602
the defense and the prosecution
have rested.

1314
01:19:46.635 --> 01:19:48.305
You've heard my instructions.

1315
01:19:48.339 --> 01:19:51.879
You're hereby dismissed
to begin deliberations.

1316
01:19:51.913 --> 01:19:53.516
Please follow the bailiff.

1317
01:19:53.549 --> 01:19:54.985
[gavel bangs]

1318
01:19:55.987 --> 01:19:57.825
So?

1319
01:19:57.858 --> 01:19:59.896
They're drowning
in reasonable doubt.

1320
01:19:59.929 --> 01:20:02.433
Acquittal. no question.

1321
01:20:02.466 --> 01:20:05.405
[intense music]

1322
01:20:13.488 --> 01:20:14.925
[instrumental music]

1323
01:20:20.202 --> 01:20:22.339
Hi. Melanie.

1324
01:20:22.373 --> 01:20:24.177
Alice Davis.
Thank you for having us.

1325
01:20:24.210 --> 01:20:25.613
Yeah. Of course.

1326
01:20:28.185 --> 01:20:31.592
<i>I just hope the jury does
the right thing for Billy.</i>

1327
01:20:31.625 --> 01:20:35.867
[Cindy] <i>Patti has fought
so hard for him.</i>

1328
01:20:35.900 --> 01:20:39.107
<i>for us. for justice.</i>

1329
01:20:39.140 --> 01:20:40.810
[man] And we're rolling.

1330
01:20:40.844 --> 01:20:44.116
It's day two
of jury deliberations.

1331
01:20:44.150 --> 01:20:47.658
You're out on bail.
a free woman.

1332
01:20:47.691 --> 01:20:52.066
staring at the very real
prospect of life in prison.

1333
01:20:53.736 --> 01:20:55.841
-The waiting must be--
-Agony.

1334
01:20:55.874 --> 01:20:59.014
-Yeah.
-What's going through your mind?

1335
01:20:59.047 --> 01:21:01.084
Patti told a good story.

1336
01:21:01.117 --> 01:21:03.054
Hell. if it were a movie.
I'd watch it.

1337
01:21:03.087 --> 01:21:06.529
<i>Melanie has been lying about
my brother for two years.</i>

1338
01:21:06.562 --> 01:21:08.933
<i>and now this trial
has been seven weeks</i>

1339
01:21:08.967 --> 01:21:11.337
<i>of nothing
but lies. lies. lies.</i>

1340
01:21:11.371 --> 01:21:14.878
<i>And it's time for a verdict of
guilty to finally shut her up.</i>

1341
01:21:15.814 --> 01:21:17.551
Joe Tacopina told a story--

1342
01:21:17.584 --> 01:21:18.953
He told the truth.

1343
01:21:18.986 --> 01:21:21.157
A version that. quite frankly.
many people

1344
01:21:21.190 --> 01:21:23.996
are having trouble believing.

1345
01:21:24.030 --> 01:21:26.703
Well. let's hope the 12 people
who matter the most

1346
01:21:26.736 --> 01:21:28.438
are smarter than that.

1347
01:21:28.471 --> 01:21:32.146
<i>I feel most for her parents.
Linda and Michael.</i>

1348
01:21:32.179 --> 01:21:33.448
<i>who I've always adored.</i>

1349
01:21:33.482 --> 01:21:36.287
<i>She's put them
in an impossible position.</i>

1350
01:21:36.321 --> 01:21:38.993
<i>What kind of a person
doesn't search</i>

1351
01:21:39.026 --> 01:21:41.197
<i>for the missing father
of her children?</i>

1352
01:21:41.231 --> 01:21:45.139
Even with all of our problems.
I desperately wanted Bill

1353
01:21:45.172 --> 01:21:49.882
to be found safe and alive.

1354
01:21:49.915 --> 01:21:52.353
<i>For weeks after Billy vanished.
I begged.</i>

1355
01:21:52.386 --> 01:21:56.027
<i>begged her to go with me
to Atlantic City.</i>

1356
01:21:56.060 --> 01:21:58.767
<i>to pressure the police there.
to make phone calls</i>

1357
01:21:58.800 --> 01:22:02.674
<i>to anyone who knew him
to help us.</i>

1358
01:22:04.343 --> 01:22:05.781
<i>She refused.</i>

1359
01:22:05.814 --> 01:22:08.051
<i>And that told me everything.</i>

1360
01:22:08.085 --> 01:22:11.325
<i>It should tell you everything.
too. Thank you.</i>

1361
01:22:11.358 --> 01:22:14.832
Finally. let me ask you
about Dr. Miller.

1362
01:22:14.865 --> 01:22:17.838
He assisted
in the effort to convict you.

1363
01:22:17.871 --> 01:22:21.579
-Do you hold it against him?
-No. No. they threatened him.

1364
01:22:21.612 --> 01:22:24.416
And he knew
I couldn't incriminate myself.

1365
01:22:24.450 --> 01:22:27.123
If you could do it
all over again.

1366
01:22:27.156 --> 01:22:30.395
would you still have the affair?

1367
01:22:30.428 --> 01:22:31.933
I don't know.

1368
01:22:31.966 --> 01:22:33.969
Do you still love him?

1369
01:22:34.337 --> 01:22:35.606
I did.

1370
01:22:37.209 --> 01:22:39.480
What do you think
happened to Bill?

1371
01:22:39.514 --> 01:22:41.985
Do you really think
he ran afoul of the mob?

1372
01:22:42.019 --> 01:22:44.257
I mean. it certainly fits.

1373
01:22:44.290 --> 01:22:45.560
Got money on the street in AC.

1374
01:22:45.593 --> 01:22:49.233
that's how you get bullets
here and here.

1375
01:22:51.070 --> 01:22:54.109
[Alice] Now. regardless
of the verdict.

1376
01:22:54.143 --> 01:22:57.984
when this program airs.
viewers are going to hear

1377
01:22:58.018 --> 01:23:01.926
claims from you that
are impossible to corroborate.

1378
01:23:01.959 --> 01:23:04.496
Why should our audience
trust you?

1379
01:23:06.969 --> 01:23:09.473
I have no control over that.

1380
01:23:10.677 --> 01:23:13.047
But I know that I'm innocent.

1381
01:23:17.991 --> 01:23:19.293
Thank you.

1382
01:23:20.329 --> 01:23:22.366
Thank you. everyone. We're done.

1383
01:23:24.003 --> 01:23:25.472
Yeah.

1384
01:23:27.176 --> 01:23:29.214
You know. I'm sure
that you get this a lot.

1385
01:23:29.247 --> 01:23:32.252
but you have
an incredible smile.

1386
01:23:33.321 --> 01:23:35.059
Uh. Bill used to say that to me.

1387
01:23:35.092 --> 01:23:39.466
"A thousand watts
of blinding light." he'd say.

1388
01:23:44.912 --> 01:23:48.117
[intense music]

1389
01:24:06.054 --> 01:24:09.326
[music continues]

1390
01:24:13.536 --> 01:24:16.508
[intense music]

1391
01:24:19.848 --> 01:24:23.756
Ladies and gentlemen.
the jury has reached a verdict.

1392
01:24:26.729 --> 01:24:30.536
I know there will be strong
feelings of both agreement...

1393
01:24:32.239 --> 01:24:33.843
and disagreement.

1394
01:24:33.876 --> 01:24:37.082
But outbursts
will not be tolerated.

1395
01:24:37.115 --> 01:24:40.422
Clerk Hacker. you may proceed.

1396
01:24:40.455 --> 01:24:43.662
Mr. Foreman. how do you find as
to the count of the indictment

1397
01:24:43.696 --> 01:24:47.369
